headline: Keysight Accelerates Electronic Design Productivity with Secure AI-Powered Assistants
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., December 16, 2025--Keysight announced AI-powered Chat and Copilot assistants for its Advanced Design System (ADS) that accelerate design workflows.
